skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ocean soundscape
Developer Terms of Use
des: Welcome to the Monterey Bay Aquarium Research Institute's Ocean Soundscape skill. I can play a live stream from Monterey Bay, or, I can play pre-recorded sounds of dolphins, killer whales, beaked whales, blue whales, fin whales, humpback whales, sperm whales, gray whales, earthquakes, or rain. As an example, you can say, "Ask Ocean Soundscape to play the live stream", or, "Ask Ocean Soundscape to play sounds of dolphins"
